　is a dungeon that you enter with
　predetermined fixed Leader & Helper.

■Rank Rewards
　Tap the [Rewards] button for more
　information.

■Dungeon Rules
・You can try the Dungeon as many
　times as you like.

・No Continues allowed.

・The [Matching Bonus] will apply
　when using the Awoken Skills below.

　[Points]    [Awoken Skills]
 　　  50 -- Two Pronged Attack
 　　 200 -- Enhanced Fire Att.
 　　 200 -- Enhanced Water Att.
 　　 200 -- Enhanced Wood Att.
 　　 200 -- Enhanced Light Att.
 　　 200 -- Enhanced Dark Att.
 　　 300 -- Bonus Attack
 　　 400 -- Guard Break
 　　 400 -- [L] Increased Attack
 　  1000 -- Damage Void Piercer
 　　1500 -- Super Bonus Attack

・You have 5 minutes to clear the
　dungeon. Past that time, your score
　will decrease every second and
　the [Matching Bonus] won't apply
　any longer.

・The [Matching Bonus] won't apply
　when Monsters or Awoken Skills
　are bound.

・You need to have the corresponding
　Awoken Skills in your team for
　the [Matching Bonus] to apply.
　For predetermined fixed team,
　please check the available Awoken
　Skills beforehand.

・When you finish a battle without
　moving any Orbs (using skills only),
　your final score will decrease.

・After entering the dungeon, if the
　device is put into sleep mode, or
　if you close the app even once, the
　dungeon may still be completed,
　but your score will not be
　registered in the ranking.

Tap the [Rules] button for more 
information about the dungeon rules.

■Warning
・Data manipulation, the use of cheating
　tools, or inappropriate user names
　will result in removal from the ranking.

　be removed from the ranking.
